        <abstract> 
<p>States he has "misgivings about the definiteness of species". Believes there is some inherent tendency for plants to originate varieties. Cross-fertilisation is likely in most cases but sees difficulties with plants like <hi rend="italic">Adlumia</hi>.</p> 
